trans-unit.source: Represents the radii of a rectangle's corners.
trans-unit.target: Representerer radier av et rektangel hjørne.

trans-unit.source: This class has four properties, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A>, corresponding to the individual corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen har fire egenskaper <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A>, og <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A>, tilsvarende til individuelle hjørne av rektanglet.</xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each is a <xref:System.Double> structure that can be set independently of the others.
trans-unit.target: Hver er en <xref:System.Double>-strukturen som kan angis uavhengig av de andre.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: The radii cannot be negative.
trans-unit.target: Radier kan ikke være negativ.

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Attribute Usage ``` - or - ``` ## XAML Values *TopLeft* value that specifies the radius of the top left corner.
trans-unit.target: ## XAML Attributtbruk ``` - or - ``` ## XAML verdier *TopLeft* verdi som angir radien til øverst venstre hjørne.

trans-unit.source: *TopRight* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the top right corner.
trans-unit.target: *TopRight* <xref:System.Double> verdi som angir øvre høyre hjørne.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *BottomRight* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: *BottomRight* <xref:System.Double> verdi som angir nedre høyre hjørne.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *BottomLeft* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the bottom left corner.
trans-unit.target: *BottomLeft* <xref:System.Double> verdi som angir nederst til venstre.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *AllCorners* If only a single <xref:System.Double> value is specified, that measure is applied to ALL of the *TopLeft*, *TopRight*, *BottomRight*, and *BottomLeft* corners of the CornerRadius.
trans-unit.target: *AllCorners* Hvis bare ett <xref:System.Double>verdi er angitt, at målet er brukt på alle de *TopLeft*, *TopRight*, *BottomRight*, og *BottomLeft* hjørne av CornerRadius.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Values need not include the decimal point explicitly when specified as a string.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Verdier må ikke inkluderer desimaltegnet eksplisitt når angitt som en streng.

trans-unit.source: The string "1" provided in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] evaluates to a value of 1.0 when referenced in code.
trans-unit.target: Strengen "1" i [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] evalueres til en verdi for 1.0 når det refereres til i koden.
